g; tower fans; and water heaters, including spa, sauna, and soul geysers. It serves various sectors, including manufacturing units, restaurants and cafes, textiles, petrochemicals, showrooms, agriculture, automobiles, retail, banquets, gym, educational, healthcare, and warehouses. The company was formerly known as Symphony Comfort Systems Limited and changed its name to Symphony Limited in March 2010. Symphony Limited was founded in 1939 and is based in Ahmedabad, India."}}